pre_text_caption_evidence: performance graph the following graph compares the cumulative five-year total return provided shareholders on our class a common stock relative to the cumulative total returns of the s&p 500 index and two customized peer groups .
the old peer group includes intercontinentalexchange , inc. , nyse euronext and the nasdaq omx group inc .
the new peer group is the same as the old peer group with the addition of cboe holdings , inc .
which completed its initial public offering in june 2010 .

an investment of $ 100 ( with reinvestment of all dividends ) is assumed to have been made in our class a common stock , in the peer groups and the s&p 500 index on december 31 , 2005 and its relative performance is tracked through december 31 , 2010 .
